(18, 1, '2014-04-23 23:35:55', '2014-04-23 13:35:55', '<p style="color: #222222;"><b>Stay and Play at the South West’s premier golf course, Sanctuary Golf Resort.</b> Twin share and quad share options. Quad share normally $575, this offer $289. Twin share available for $198, normally $396.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222;"><a style="color: #3333cc;" href="http://crazygolfdeals.com.au/deal/national--2/stay-and-play-at-sanctuary-golf-resort-wa-twin-share" target="_blank"><b><span class="caps">FOR</span> <span class="caps">TWIN</span> <span class="caps">SHARE</span> <span class="caps">STAY</span> AT $198, <span class="caps">CLICK</span> <span class="caps">HERE</span>.</b></a></p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222;"><b>Quad Share Option includes:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: #222222;">\r\n	<li>Overnight accommodation in a 2 bedroom apartment for up to 4 adults</li>\r\n	<li>Continental breakfast for 4</li>\r\n	<li>4x 18 holes of golf (carts <span class="caps">NOT</span> included)</li>\r\n	<li>A jug of beer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="color: #222222;">Value: $575, this offer $289 (that’s just $72 per person!).</p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222;"><strong style="color: #f05b26;">Sanctuary Golf Resort</strong>\r\nSituated on 37 hectares of rolling green lawns and tranquil lakes, the Sanctuary Golf Resort is nestled in the heart of the Geographe Wine Region and is a great location for leisurely golf and relaxation.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #222222;">Nestled amongst landscaped gardens, fairways and a multitude of of local birdlife, the Sanctuary Golf Resort offers contemporary apartment accommodation with views of the pool, landscaped gardens or golf course. All rates include complimentary parking, Foxtel and wireless broadband. <i>More information below and at:</i><a style="color: #3333cc;" href="http://www.sanctuaryresort.com.au/" target="_blank"><b>www.sanctuaryresort.com.au</b></a></p>', '18 Holes at Woolooware for 2 plus 2 drinks and a cart', '<h3>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</h3>', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-holes-at-woolooware-for-2-plus-2-drinks-and-a-cart', '', '', '2014-04-29 00:30:22', '2014-04-28 14:30:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/GitHub/GGD_Site_V1_0/?product=18-holes-at-woolooware-for-2-plus-2-drinks-and-a-cart', 0, 'product', '', 0),
